<Link id="l00756" /><CodeLine lineNumber="756"></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00757" /><CodeLine lineNumber="757"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// This function checks to see if an expansion of memcmp can be generated.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00758" /><CodeLine lineNumber="758"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// It checks for constant compare size that is less than the max inline size.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00759" /><CodeLine lineNumber="759"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// If an expansion cannot occur, returns false to leave as a library call.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00760" /><CodeLine lineNumber="760"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// Otherwise, the library call is replaced with a new IR instruction sequence.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00761" /><CodeLine lineNumber="761"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// We want to transform:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00762" /><CodeLine lineNumber="762"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// %call = call signext i32 @memcmp(i8&#42; %0, i8&#42; %1, i64 15)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00763" /><CodeLine lineNumber="763"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// To:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00764" /><CodeLine lineNumber="764"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// loadbb:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00765" /><CodeLine lineNumber="765"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///  %0 = bitcast i32&#42; %buffer2 to i8&#42;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00766" /><CodeLine lineNumber="766"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///  %1 = bitcast i32&#42; %buffer1 to i8&#42;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00767" /><CodeLine lineNumber="767"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///  %2 = bitcast i8&#42; %1 to i64&#42;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00768" /><CodeLine lineNumber="768"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///  %3 = bitcast i8&#42; %0 to i64&#42;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00769" /><CodeLine lineNumber="769"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///  %4 = load i64, i64&#42; %2</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00770" /><CodeLine lineNumber="770"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///  %5 = load i64, i64&#42; %3</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00771" /><CodeLine lineNumber="771"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///  %6 = call i64 @llvm.bswap.i64(i64 %4)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00772" /><CodeLine lineNumber="772"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///  %7 = call i64 @llvm.bswap.i64(i64 %5)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00773" /><CodeLine lineNumber="773"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///  %8 = sub i64 %6, %7</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00774" /><CodeLine lineNumber="774"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///  %9 = icmp ne i64 %8, 0</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00775" /><CodeLine lineNumber="775"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///  br i1 %9, label %res&#95;block, label %loadbb1</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00776" /><CodeLine lineNumber="776"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// res&#95;block:                                        ; preds = %loadbb2,</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00777" /><CodeLine lineNumber="777"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// %loadbb1, %loadbb</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00778" /><CodeLine lineNumber="778"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///  %phi.src1 = phi i64 &#91; %6, %loadbb &#93;, &#91; %22, %loadbb1 &#93;, &#91; %36, %loadbb2 &#93;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00779" /><CodeLine lineNumber="779"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///  %phi.src2 = phi i64 &#91; %7, %loadbb &#93;, &#91; %23, %loadbb1 &#93;, &#91; %37, %loadbb2 &#93;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00780" /><CodeLine lineNumber="780"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///  %10 = icmp ult i64 %phi.src1, %phi.src2</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00781" /><CodeLine lineNumber="781"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///  %11 = select i1 %10, i32 -1, i32 1</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00782" /><CodeLine lineNumber="782"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///  br label %endblock</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00783" /><CodeLine lineNumber="783"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// loadbb1:                                          ; preds = %loadbb</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00784" /><CodeLine lineNumber="784"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///  %12 = bitcast i32&#42; %buffer2 to i8&#42;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00785" /><CodeLine lineNumber="785"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///  %13 = bitcast i32&#42; %buffer1 to i8&#42;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00786" /><CodeLine lineNumber="786"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///  %14 = bitcast i8&#42; %13 to i32&#42;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00787" /><CodeLine lineNumber="787"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///  %15 = bitcast i8&#42; %12 to i32&#42;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00788" /><CodeLine lineNumber="788"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///  %16 = getelementptr i32, i32&#42; %14, i32 2</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00789" /><CodeLine lineNumber="789"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///  %17 = getelementptr i32, i32&#42; %15, i32 2</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00790" /><CodeLine lineNumber="790"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///  %18 = load i32, i32&#42; %16</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00791" /><CodeLine lineNumber="791"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///  %19 = load i32, i32&#42; %17</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00792" /><CodeLine lineNumber="792"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///  %20 = call i32 @llvm.bswap.i32(i32 %18)</span></CodeLine>
